trans-unit.source: Defines the binding element used to create a custom peer resolver.
trans-unit.target: Define o elemento de enlace utilizado para criar uma resolução de peer personalizado.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new default instance of the <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Channels.PeerCustomResolverBindingElement"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância predefinida do <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Channels.PeerCustomResolverBindingElement"> </xref> classe.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Channels.PeerCustomResolverBindingElement"></xref> class by cloning the provided custom peer resolver binding.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância do <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Channels.PeerCustomResolverBindingElement"> </xref> classe através da clonagem o Resolvedor de elemento personalizado fornecido enlace.

trans-unit.source: <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Channels.PeerCustomResolverBindingElement"></xref> instance which contains the settings to clone for the new binding.
trans-unit.target: <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Channels.PeerCustomResolverBindingElement"></xref>instância que contém as definições para clonar para o novo enlace.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Channels.PeerCustomResolverBindingElement"></xref> class with the provided resolver settings.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância do <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Channels.PeerCustomResolverBindingElement"> </xref> classe com as definições de resolução fornecido.

trans-unit.source: <xref href="System.ServiceModel.PeerResolvers.PeerCustomResolverSettings"></xref> object that contains the specific settings for the new binding.
trans-unit.target: <xref href="System.ServiceModel.PeerResolvers.PeerCustomResolverSettings"></xref>objeto que contém as definições específicas para o novo enlace.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Channels.PeerCustomResolverBindingElement"></xref> class with the provided binding context and resolver settings.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância do <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Channels.PeerCustomResolverBindingElement"> </xref> classe com as definições de contexto e resolução de enlace fornecido.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.BindingContext> object that contains the binding context for resolvers created by this binding.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.BindingContext>objeto que contém o contexto de enlace para resoluções criadas por este enlace.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.BindingContext>

trans-unit.source: Gets and sets the endpoint address of the peer on which resolvers created by this binding will run.
trans-unit.target: Obtém e define o endereço de ponto final do elemento de rede em que serão executadas resoluções criadas por este enlace.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.ServiceModel.EndpointAddress> object that contains the network address of the peer on which resolvers created by this binding will run.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.ServiceModel.EndpointAddress>objeto que contém o endereço de rede do elemento de rede em que serão executadas resoluções criadas por este enlace.</xref:System.ServiceModel.EndpointAddress>

trans-unit.source: Gets and sets the network binding used by resolvers created with this binding element.
